                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1" corresp="#h2">
                                        <locus from="224v" to="226v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3052RepCh332">Hymn to David</title></desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">እምሥርወ፡ ዕሴይ፡ እስመ፡ ሠረፅከ፡ ወእማኅፀና፡ ለሩት። ናስተበፅዓከ፡ ዘልፈ፡ በንባበ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ስብሐት። 
                                        ኦብፁዕ፡ ንጉሠ፡ እስራኤል፡ ዳዊት። ሶበ፡ ተከሥተ፡ ወተረከበ፡ ባሕርየ፡ ውሣጣይ፡ ሕይወት። እመዝገበ፡ ከርሣ፡ ለማርያም፡ ዘለከ፡ ሕይወት። ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ 
                                        ስምከ፡ ውስተ፡ ረቀ፡ መዝሙር፡ ዘተዌደደ።
                                   </seg></q>
                                 </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#226v"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">A note gave the name of a later owner, for which that of 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13080Isayeyyas">ʾIsāyǝyyās</persName> has been substituted.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#227r"/>
                                    <desc type="Unclear">Note in Amharic.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="am"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <locus target="#2v"/>
                                    <desc>The names originally mentioned in the manuscript have been erased, 
                                        only that of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13081WalattaH">Walatta Hāymānot</persName> is still legible.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e2">
                                    <locus target="#82r"/>
                                    <desc>The names originally mentioned in the manuscript are partially legible. One ended by 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክርስቶስ&gt;</foreign>, which has been changed into 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13079HellaweK">Hǝllāwe Krǝstos</persName>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e3">
                                    <locus target="#2v"/>
                                    <desc>The names originally mentioned in the manuscript have been erased,
                                       and substituted by those of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13082KidanaM">Kidāna Māryām</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13080Isayeyyas">ʾIsāyǝyyās</persName>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e4">
                                    <locus target="#82r"/>
                                    <desc>The name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13083TaklaAl">Takla ʾAlfā</persName>, brother of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13080Isayeyyas">ʾIsāyǝyyās</persName>, 
                                    is mentioned.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e5">
                                    <locus target="#159v"/>
                                    <desc>The name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13084TaklaAb">Takla ʾAbbā</persName>, brother of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13080Isayeyyas">ʾIsāyǝyyās</persName>, 
                                        is mentioned.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e6">
                                    <locus target="#217r"/>
                                    <desc>The name of the scribe, <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13085WaldaH">Walda Hāymānot</persName>, 
                                        is mentioned at the end of <ref target="#ms_i6"/>.</desc>
                                </item>
                            </list>
                            
